headline: Agilent to Announce First-Quarter Fiscal Year 2026 Financial Results on Feb. 25
summary: SANTA CLARA, Calif., February 02, 2026--Agilent Technologies Inc. (NYSE: A) will release financial results for the first quarter of fiscal year 2026 after the stock market closes on Wednesday, Feb. 25. The company will host a conference call to discuss the results at 1:30 p.m. PST the same day.
